properties.note: Wooden sign stating "macomb Mt" is the peak.

properties.name: South Dix
properties.note: Peak is a tree with carving "S Dix" and a very small circle placard above eye level on the same tree.

properties.name: Grace Peak
properties.note: absolutely gorgeous views;about 45/way from S. Dix.

properties.name: Cliff Mountain
properties.note: Trail ends at summit with a signpost and no views on the wooded summit.

properties.description: Highest Mountain in New York State
properties.name: Mount Marcy
Garden Parking Area
properties.description: Fee is $10/day (2017). Overflow parking is at Marcy Field. Shuttle service ($10/person/round-trip; 2017) runs from Marcy Field to Garden (June 17 through October 15 on Saturdays, Sundays, and Holidays; 7:00 AM to 7:00 PM).

properties.name: Ausable Club Parking Area (Reservation Required)
properties.description: Also known as St Huberts Parking area. Access for trailheads to Upper & Lower Wolfjaws, Phelps, Tabletop, Sawteeeth, Gothics, Armstrong, Dial, Nippletop, Colvin, Blake, and the Dix Range. If full, there is no overflow parking on the 73.
